{"tid":1757514,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"連仔可唔可以係時事台開多個區議會分類？","createTime":"2019-11-26T14:24:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T08:51:51.000Z","uid":26908,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ea3a45b9e3f29720bd4448d04d410913b59d8b84","tid":1757514,"uid":26908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:24:24.000Z","msg":"選舉結束，大批素人當選區議員，入面有學生、大學fresh grad 、後生打工仔。都有個共通點係冇經驗冇人脈冇團隊。<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日眼見時事台有唔小討論區政既post：有前輩經驗、有創新構想、有人力資源建議。班後生區議員會睇連登睇post搵攻略應該都幾普遍，連仔如果可以開多個分類，會唔會令交流可以順暢啲？<br />\n<br />\n區議員可以黎招募諮詢、連登手足又可以主動建言。連登卧虎藏龍，想必對區議員工作有所助益。"},{"pid":"cd8947a86521a11fae92b011328817d320865c1e","tid":1757514,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T14:25:10.000Z","msg":"怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9cf4c132bf2dd98cbb93dfc1b5ef0a3b25e9aeeb","tid":1757514,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:34:25.000Z","msg":"不如政事台？好似比較適合"},{"pid":"c916baa6227d4a95ab42da62ff4033d5ea9018ac","tid":1757514,"uid":26908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cf4c132bf2dd98cbb93dfc1b5ef0a3b25e9aeeb","tid":1757514,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:34:25.000Z","msg":"不如政事台？好似比較適合"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T07:14:20.000Z","msg":"時事台人多啲，可以比較多討論"},{"pid":"ffc9f843aa42f493eaff6ca7e9f39362c4da02ac","tid":1757514,"uid":101345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T08:36:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b801ed271a8a8fea3c3f1f48244ac100d5eb688f","tid":1757514,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c916baa6227d4a95ab42da62ff4033d5ea9018ac","tid":1757514,"uid":26908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cf4c132bf